review_text: This park is considered to be big in Roxboro, with a few mini soccer fields and playground. Benches were built by the side with one dedicated to Mr Gray. I would like to learn more about the stories behind. Please tell me.
They really need to cut the grass and get rid of weeds.

(Translated by Google) Good park with soccer field. But the toilets are not very clean.

(Original)
Bon parc avec terrain de soccer. Mais les toilettes ne sont pas très propres.
